      "content": {
        "title": "Properties of Definite Integrals",
        "definition": "Linearity, additivity over intervals, reversal of limits changing sign, and comparison properties governing manipulation of ∫_a^b f(x) dx.",
        "summary": "Integral properties allow splitting domains, combining integrands, and estimating values without explicit antiderivatives."
      },
